-- ‘Toy Story 3’ Nominated for Golden Globe Best Animated Feature
-- B y   M i c h a e l   W h i t e
-- 2010-12-14T13:34:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-14/-toy-story-3-nominated-for-golden-globe-award-for-best-animated-feature.html
“Toy Story 3” and “Despicable
Me” were among films nominated for Golden Globe awards for the
best animated feature film of 2010.  The five nominees also included “How to Train Your
Dragon” “The Illusionist” and “Tangled,” the Hollywood
Foreign Press Association said today during a news conference in
Beverly Hills, California.  To contact the reporter on this story:
